{"tid":1280862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班巨人已經冇感情 要死都斬死一兩件先去死","createTime":"2019-07-03T06:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:20:34.000Z","uid":80483,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c069aa70891354984388109015d046d365b1c7de","tid":1280862,"uid":80483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"各位新兵記住<br />\n唔好因為巨人本身係人而心軟<br />\n佢哋已經冇哂感情<br />\n你喺高牆跳落去只會變成佢哋嘅食糧<br />\n要做嘅係減少人力消耗<br />\n依家調查兵團唔夠人<br />\n更加要入團去幫手<br />\n你哋唔好諗住要兵長一個殺哂<br />\n你哋都可以去斬巨人<br />\n唔好睇少自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斬哂所有巨人 打敗極權國家 人類是自由的"},{"pid":"7eeb295f2dee82fb6109623c7907468879c9b728","tid":1280862,"uid":103585,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d2bb94d7b8670ff9fb89192d76234c2c9d3b67a","tid":1280862,"uid":80483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"開錯台 唔理了<br />\n<br />\n本來我都想以死相揀<br />\n<br />\n但已經決定咗同戰士們齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n要死都只會係喺同巨人打杖嘅時候死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 睇巨人睇上腦 中二病發作"},{"pid":"9e874fa5b21276a9c73191c0b93710f13c194bb1","tid":1280862,"uid":80483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"人手幫推 調查兵團需要你"},{"pid":"a4fee57bac4012bce6c06a483e13ab80fbf784a9","tid":1280862,"uid":124133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcacb6d68abed9fcfb3305c35e238bf173e43ee","tid":1280862,"uid":80483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5f86f5ed7f01a220f97ab738d4ae92d102a149a","tid":1280862,"uid":80483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:25:35.000Z","msg":"調查兵團要人呀"},{"pid":"8c29b7e6d84a16f796a1d641209bd98c814faa63","tid":1280862,"uid":80483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:04:04.000Z","msg":"<